<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 18:10:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列战争第 248 天：联合国安理会将就支持停战提案的决议进行投票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-248-un-security-council-to-vote-on-resolution-backing-truce-proposal/00000190-02f5-de5e-a5ff-27f793a90001</link><description>据报道，拜登政府正在讨论与哈马斯达成协议，以防涉及以色列的谈判失败，释放被关押在加沙的五名美国公民 ■ 美国国务卿布林肯自 10 月 7 日以来第八次访问以色列 ■ 联合国安理会将就美国决议进行投票支持拜登提出的停战提案 ■ 一架以色列无人机在黎巴嫩被击落 ■ 战争进入 248 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-248-un-security-council-to-vote-on-resolution-backing-truce-proposal/00000190-02f5-de5e-a5ff-27f793a90001</guid></item><item><title>忘记反犹太复国主义者吧。让我们成为反卡汉主义者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/forget-being-anti-zionists-lets-be-anti-kahanists/00000190-0228-d660-af95-6fbed3e60000</link><description>世界各地校园里关于反犹太复国主义及其与反犹太主义的关系的语义烟花分散了我们需要进行的辩论的注意力。真正的危险是以色列种族主义极右翼力量的不断增长及其对以色列人、巴勒斯坦人和散居海外的犹太人造成的后果</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:45:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/forget-being-anti-zionists-lets-be-anti-kahanists/00000190-0228-d660-af95-6fbed3e60000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列边境警察被控“无缘无故”向巴勒斯坦人投掷手榴弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/two-border-policemen-charged-with-throwing-grenade-at-palestinian-for-no-reason/00000190-02c8-d5ad-ad93-26c913a00000</link><description>由于警察的行动，这名巴勒斯坦男子的一只眼睛失明了，据称这种行为是“没有任何正当理由”的。尽管行为严重，但仍决定以最高可判处三年监禁的罪名起诉他们</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/two-border-policemen-charged-with-throwing-grenade-at-palestinian-for-no-reason/00000190-02c8-d5ad-ad93-26c913a00000</guid></item><item><title>“带他们回家”：以色列人在希腊酷玩乐队演唱会上即兴高歌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/bring-them-home-israelis-lead-impromptu-chant-at-coldplay-concert-in-greece/00000190-0299-d660-af95-6fbf283d0000</link><description>周六，以色列军队勇敢地营救了四名人质，随后参加酷玩乐队雅典演出的以色列人齐声高喊，呼吁释放哈马斯囚禁中的剩余人质。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:22:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/bring-them-home-israelis-lead-impromptu-chant-at-coldplay-concert-in-greece/00000190-0299-d660-af95-6fbf283d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长斯莫特里奇告诉人质家属潜在的交易是“集体自杀”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-finance-minister-tells-hostages-families-potential-deal-is-collective-suicide/00000190-029e-de5e-a5ff-279e3ccb0000</link><description>极右翼部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇告诉人质家属，以色列将“不遗余力”营救他们的亲人，但强调他不会支持与哈马斯达成任何包括结束战争的协议</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-finance-minister-tells-hostages-families-potential-deal-is-collective-suicide/00000190-029e-de5e-a5ff-279e3ccb0000</guid></item><item><title>“太糟糕了，你回来了”：被释放的以色列人质说她收到了负面评论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/too-bad-you-returned-freed-israeli-hostage-says-shes-received-negative-comments/00000190-0151-da02-a1dc-fd5b38f00000</link><description>阿加姆·戈尔茨坦-阿尔莫格与她的母亲和兄弟一起从卡法阿扎基布兹被绑架到加沙。她说公众不喜欢她描述自己与绑架者的关系，而且“人们无法理解”作为人质的感受</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 15:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/too-bad-you-returned-freed-israeli-hostage-says-shes-received-negative-comments/00000190-0151-da02-a1dc-fd5b38f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列专家称英国报纸对哈马斯性暴力的评论断章取义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-experts-say-u-k-newspaper-took-comments-on-hamas-sexual-violence-out-of-context/00000190-023b-dbe3-a1da-133f981a0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，三名积极反对哈马斯强奸和性暴力否认的以色列人在社交媒体上进行了反击，声称他们对一篇有关性别暴力的文章发表的评论被视为“愤世嫉俗的剥削”</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 14:51:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-experts-say-u-k-newspaper-took-comments-on-hamas-sexual-violence-out-of-context/00000190-023b-dbe3-a1da-133f981a0000</guid></item><item><title>司法部命令总理办公室删除有关萨拉·内塔尼亚胡与人质家属会谈的推文</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/pms-office-ordered-to-remove-tweets-about-sara-netanyahus-talks-with-hostages-families/00000190-023e-d5ad-ad93-267f8e980000</link><description>司法部解释说，这些帖子违反了政策，该政策规定总理的官方账户不应被用来讨论当选领导人配偶的个人活动，除非总理本人也参与其中</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 13:43:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/pms-office-ordered-to-remove-tweets-about-sara-netanyahus-talks-with-hostages-families/00000190-023e-d5ad-ad93-267f8e980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预计极右翼在欧洲议会的胜利将驳回对加沙战争的批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-expects-far-right-gains-in-european-parliament-will-improve-its-standing/00000190-01eb-dd57-abb4-7beb32460000</link><description>绿党的衰弱和极右翼政党（尤其是法国和德国）的重大进展，可能会帮助以色列拒绝有利于巴勒斯坦人的重大措施。以色列希望新任欧盟外长的政策不会对其持批评态度</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 13:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-expects-far-right-gains-in-european-parliament-will-improve-its-standing/00000190-01eb-dd57-abb4-7beb32460000</guid></item><item><title>七种芝士蛋糕食谱，让您的五旬节客人眼花缭乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-10/ty-article/the-top-seven-recipes-for-a-sweet-shavuot/0000017f-e722-df5f-a17f-fffe1d5e0000</link><description>如果没有一块不起眼的——或者不那么不起眼的——芝士蛋糕，五旬节餐就不完整。今年有一些甜、酸、咸的食谱值得尝试</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 13:28:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-10/ty-article/the-top-seven-recipes-for-a-sweet-shavuot/0000017f-e722-df5f-a17f-fffe1d5e0000</guid></item><item><title>“一名妇女或她的胎儿可能有危险，但她不会去医院”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-woman-or-her-fetus-could-be-in-danger-but-she-wont-go-to-the-hospital/0000018f-e74b-d11f-a5cf-e7cba5b90000</link><description>对于以色列南部的贝都因妇女来说，怀孕会带来许多问题，自 10 月 7 日以来这些问题有增无减。新的分娩准备课程旨在帮助她们更好地为产房做好准备。该倡议背后的女性表示，“知识就是力量”，她强调该倡议并不是为了教导女性成为“好病人”</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 13:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-woman-or-her-fetus-could-be-in-danger-but-she-wont-go-to-the-hospital/0000018f-e74b-d11f-a5cf-e7cba5b90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列研究显示，社交媒体巨头在 10 月 7 日之后未能删除虚假内容</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/social-media-giants-fail-to-remove-conspirative-content-after-oct-7-israeli-study-shows/0000018f-fd4a-de5e-a5ef-fdce63770000</link><description>以色列互联网协会声称，Facebook、Instagram、X、YouTube和TikTok没有充分遏制有关哈马斯袭击和加沙战争的阴谋论和虚假信息，并且无视用户的投诉</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 12:51:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/social-media-giants-fail-to-remove-conspirative-content-after-oct-7-israeli-study-shows/0000018f-fd4a-de5e-a5ef-fdce63770000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会将对内塔尼亚胡推动的豁免法案草案进行投票；勇于反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-vote-on-draft-exemption-bill-pushed-by-netanyahu-gallant-to-oppose/00000190-0164-d5ad-ad93-256d30c00000</link><description>上个月，内塔尼亚胡开始推动最初在拉皮德-贝内特政府领导下提交的豁免法案草案，尽管司法部长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉表示反对，称该法案不适合以色列加沙战争的当前现实。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-vote-on-draft-exemption-bill-pushed-by-netanyahu-gallant-to-oppose/00000190-0164-d5ad-ad93-256d30c00000</guid></item><item><title>柏林犹太以色列餐厅自 10 月 7 日起关门 20 年后即将关门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/closed-since-october-7-berlins-kosher-israeli-restaurant-is-folding-after-20-years/00000190-0172-dbe3-a1da-11778efb0000</link><description>Bleibergs 的老板表示，他最终决定永久关闭餐厅，部分原因是人们“在柏林看起来像一个虔诚的犹太人，感觉不舒服”</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:15:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/closed-since-october-7-berlins-kosher-israeli-restaurant-is-folding-after-20-years/00000190-0172-dbe3-a1da-11778efb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列盟友担心甘茨的离开将加强政府中的极端分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-allies-worry-gantzs-departure-will-strengthen-extremists-in-the-government/00000190-00f1-da02-a1dc-fcfb25ae0000</link><description>一位亲以色列国家的外交官表示，甘茨和艾森科特退出后，国防部长加兰特是内阁中唯一值得信赖的伙伴，因为西方政府拒绝与斯莫特里奇和本格维尔有任何关系，并对内塔尼亚胡产生怀疑。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-allies-worry-gantzs-departure-will-strengthen-extremists-in-the-government/00000190-00f1-da02-a1dc-fcfb25ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方对交通部可能存在的欺诈和失信行为展开调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-launches-investigation-into-transportation-ministers-corruption-allegations/00000190-0195-da02-a1dc-fddf14af0001</link><description>警方在以色列总检察长的指示下表示，在电视曝光米里·雷格夫部长优先考虑可以在利库德集团初选中帮助她的地方政府后，调查人员抵达耶路撒冷交通部，搜查了该地方并没收了文件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-launches-investigation-into-transportation-ministers-corruption-allegations/00000190-0195-da02-a1dc-fddf14af0001</guid></item><item><title>由于美国担心与哈马斯的谈判破裂，布林肯将登陆以色列以推进人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/as-u-s-fears-collapse-of-talks-blinken-to-land-in-israel-to-advance-hostage-deal/00000190-014c-dbe3-a1da-116d908f0000</link><description>布林肯访问的主要目标是推进释放人质和停火协议，拜登政府大约一周半前提出了该协议，但尚未得到哈马斯的正式回应</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 09:27:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/as-u-s-fears-collapse-of-talks-blinken-to-land-in-israel-to-advance-hostage-deal/00000190-014c-dbe3-a1da-116d908f0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争期间：出售给以色列的塞尔维亚武器大量增加，并由以色列军机空运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/during-gaza-war-spike-in-serbian-arms-sold-to-israel-flown-in-on-israeli-military-planes/0000018f-e842-dc46-a5bf-f8c625370000</link><description>BIRN 和国土报的联合调查发现，以色列空军有 7 架航班从塞尔维亚起飞，恰逢塞尔维亚向以色列出口价值 1570 万欧元的武器激增</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 07:49:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/during-gaza-war-spike-in-serbian-arms-sold-to-israel-flown-in-on-israeli-military-planes/0000018f-e842-dc46-a5bf-f8c625370000</guid></item><item><title>美国国务卿布林肯抵达以色列会见总理内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-live/idf-aerial-target-intercepted-in-north-after-rocket-sirens-activated-near-haifa/00000190-0027-dd57-abb4-7a6fd30f0000</link><description>NBC 报道称，美国与哈马斯讨论了一项将以色列排除在外的单方面人质协议 ■ 斯莫特里奇部长表示，他不会支持停火协议，因为这是“集体自杀” ■ 《华尔街日报》报道称，美国和沙特阿拉伯即将敲定国防条款条约 ■ 基布兹北部住宅被黎巴嫩火箭弹击中起火 ■ 以色列国防军在约旦河西岸开展反恐行动；消息人士称，两名巴勒斯坦人被杀，其中包括一名青年。 ■ 定居者的拖车在约旦河西岸被纵火；以色列国防军怀疑纵火</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 03:40:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-live/idf-aerial-target-intercepted-in-north-after-rocket-sirens-activated-near-haifa/00000190-0027-dd57-abb4-7a6fd30f0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管营救行动取得成功，但以色列国防官员一致认为，协议是遣返剩余人质的最佳方式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-officials-believe-a-deal-is-the-best-way-to-return-remaining-hostages/0000018f-fe80-d5ad-ad8f-fec907ba0000</link><description>以色列军队很快就会对哈马斯在加沙的24个领土旅造成重大打击，这可能为停火创造条件。决定其可能性的主要因素是双方的意愿——这似乎并不高</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 03:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-officials-believe-a-deal-is-the-best-way-to-return-remaining-hostages/0000018f-fe80-d5ad-ad8f-fec907ba0000</guid></item></channel></rss>